title: Dream - Minecraft Hitmen Extra Scenes (Hitmen 2)
author: DreamXD
description:
This is extra scenes from Dream's channel of the "Minecraft Survivor VS 3 Hitmen" video. We react to what happened during the video and talk about it.
Manhunt Merch: https://www.dream.shop

Original Video: https://youtu.be/hgdSJdeGF_0 on  @Dream 

This video was crazy fun and intense. Definitely one of the hardest challenges.

Minecraft challenge videos are fun to do :)
